
" [When there is a previous search pattern, highlight all its matches](https://vimhelp.org/options.txt.html#%27hlsearch%27)
set hlsearch

" [Ignore case in search patterns](https://vimhelp.org/options.txt.html#%27ignorecase%27)
set ignorecase

" [While typing a search command, show where the pattern, as it was typed so far, matches. The matched string is highlighted](https://vimhelp.org/options.txt.html#%27incsearch%27)
set incsearch

" [Tenths of a second to show the matching paren, when 'showmatch' is](https://vimhelp.org/options.txt.html#%27matchtime%27)
set matchtime=2

" [When a bracket is inserted, briefly jump to the matching one. The jump is only done if the match can be seen on the screen. The time to show the match can be set with 'matchtime'](https://vimhelp.org/options.txt.html#%27showmatch%27)
set showmatch

" [Override the 'ignorecase' option if the search pattern contains upper case characters. Only used when the search pattern is typed and 'ignorecase' option is on](https://vimhelp.org/options.txt.html#%27smartcase%27)
set smartcase
